in_fqfn = create_complex_test_file(self.temp_dir, header=False)
dialect = csvhelper.Dialect(delimiter=',', quoting=csv.QUOTE_NONE,
    quotechar=None, has_header=False, doublequote=False)
out_fqfn = in_fqfn + '.sorted'
cmd = f""" {pjoin(SCRIPT_DIR, 'gristle_sorter')}                       -i {in_fqfn}
                    -o {out_fqfn}
                    -k 0ir 1sf
              """
executor(cmd, expect_success=True)
actual_recs = get_file_contents(out_fqfn, dialect)
expected_recs = [['4', 'aaa', 'a23'], ['4', 'aba', 'a23'], ['4', 'bbb',
    'a23'], ['3', 'aaa', 'b23'], ['3', 'aaa', 'b23'], ['1', 'aaa', 'a23']]
pp(actual_recs)
assert actual_recs == expected_recs
